    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_920915073034937760.png",
                "id": "talent94557",
                "key": "神代射術",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神代射術"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">風域</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">風域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方執行「切換角色」行動時：</span>少花費1個元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/5462e680a1901ee99a16d6f6476e47a9_1187016250565423184.png",
                "id": "talent74892",
                "key": "高天之歌",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "高天之歌"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">暴風之眼</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/4e6c64424bb066f0f74936bf7fbc1b5a_1030834172659152431.png",
                "id": "talent93820",
                "key": "風神之詩",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風神之詩"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>，對方切換到<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">距離我方出戰角色最近的角色</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方角色或召喚物引發擴散反應後：</span>轉換此牌的元素類型，改為造成被擴散的元素類型的傷害。（離場前僅限一次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_655116769476444117.png",
                "key": "暴風之眼",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/481ff844d1ba46461024c9ade7a0e5db_5432169468646192230.png",
                "title": "暴風之眼"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（冰）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點冰元素傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（水）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點水元素傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（火）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點火元素傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（雷）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點雷元素傷害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_8714197497498640430.png",
                "key": "風元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">距離我方出戰角色最近的角色</span></strong></p><p>對方場上距離我方出戰角色「最近」的角色，指的是位置與我方出戰角色最接近的敵方角色。</p><p>如果存在多個位置最接近的角色，則其中靠前的角色被視為「最近」。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3406338427551004368.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
